name: Without a phone
description:
Have you ever experienced a moment without your phone & internet, because someone accidently took it 😳
I felt really weird.😅 It was like I couldn't be found, I was lost for over 6 hours😱. And everybody was looking for me. But I must tell you it was a really relaxing moment. I was expected to be in sevrage and it wasn't like that 🍂🍁💥

This comic strip was created for inktober 2021, day 21.

Animated video, size 1080 x 1110
